'''Brahim Izri''' d anaẓur n ccna atrar azwaw, ilul ass n 12 yennayer 1954 deg taddart At Laḥsen deg [[Ayt Yanni]], di temnaṭ d [[Tizi Wezzu]]. Imut ass n 3 yennayer 2005 si sbiṭar 'Hôtel-Dieu' di '[[Paris]]', s yiwen n lehlak n Cancer umhares.
 	
Brahim Izri ilmed aẓawan di zawiya Sidi Belqasem, i gellan d jedd-is s baba-s.

